          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-1" n="1">Beneath this verdant hillock lies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-2" n="2">Demar, the wealthy &amp; the wise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-5" n="5">His heirs that he may safely rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-6" n="6">Have put his carcase in a chest;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-7" n="7">The very Chest, in which they say,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-8" n="8">Is other self, his Money, lay.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-9" n="9">And, if his heirs continue kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-10" n="10">To that dear self he left behind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-11" n="11">I dare believe, that four in five</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-700B-line-12" n="12">Will think his better half alive.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
